{"tid":189160,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"[有圖][求救] 相信大家細個既時候都玩過Hangman","createTime":"2017-04-06T08:38:29.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-06T08:54:46.000Z","uid":26931,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"2db75bbf7c6da93126ef3b99b1d6eda502f8303a","tid":189160,"uid":26931,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-06T08:38:29.000Z","msg":"細個番學上堂, 其中一隻最常玩既game應該係hangman, 如果冇記錯, 張圖應該係咁畫既<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oQxPN7s.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FoQxPN7s.png&h=94724fb8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n但當慢慢大過, 就會開始覺得好唔合理, 有乜可能吊頸會就咁吊住個頭, 咁樣點睇都係會扯斷d頭髮先, 於是, 我就慢慢轉左畫法, 變左咁<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2r89909.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2r89909.png&h=d964e105&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n如是者玩左幾年, 有一次同個讀art既同學玩, 佢話我太天真, 建議至少要畫到咁既level先有資格玩<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WS97S52.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWS97S52.png&h=a71938f8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n好,於是我就跟佢畫, 但有一次, 我有個讀哲學既同學, 話hangman其實好唔合乎邏輯, 因為張圖完全反映唔到人面臨死亡時既個種生理現象同掙扎, 所以佢話要加多d效果先得<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/m3K9HT0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fm3K9HT0.jpg&h=e1e2a87f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n過幾日, 我就要去d侄仔屋企度交佢地玩, 但我已經分唔到點樣先可以畫到一幅完美既hangman, 求巴打提供一幅最合理又最有型既圖比我參考下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f8683ef2615f9a1ea134e13a68cd62bf289ac0ca","tid":189160,"uid":46642,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-06T08:41:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/5/5f/Ahoracado_%28juego%29_-_2.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fcommons%2F5%2F5f%2FAhoracado_%2528juego%2529_-_2.gif&h=6745026c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ee367ebbd27e9695